<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-purple);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Sectors</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Hospitality &amp; Leisure</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Hotels, restaurants, bars, gyms and visitor attractions live or die on the guest experience — so building services have to land fast, to brand standard, and around live trading. We bring MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works together under one accountable team, so rooms, covers and revenue come back online on the date you planned for. No surprises in front of guests.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Hospitality &amp; Leisure →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">Across every trade</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Four service lines,<br>under one team.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span><a href="/meph/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">MEPH</a></span></h4><ul><li>HVAC, comfort cooling &amp; ventilation</li><li>Commercial kitchen extract &amp; make-up air</li><li>Power, lighting &amp; feature lighting</li><li>Hot &amp; cold water services</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span><a href="/commercial/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Commercial Fit-out</a></span></h4><ul><li>Front &amp; back of house</li><li>Guest rooms &amp; bedroom fit-out</li><li>Bars, restaurants &amp; service areas</li><li>Brand-standard finishes &amp; joinery</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span><a href="/fabric/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Fabric</a></span></h4><ul><li>Façade &amp; signage zones</li><li>Roofing &amp; weatherproofing</li><li>Glazing &amp; shopfronts</li><li>Weatherproofing &amp; thermal upgrades</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Landscaping</a></span></h4><ul><li>Terraces &amp; external dining</li><li>Entrances &amp; arrival sequence</li><li>Planting &amp; soft landscaping</li><li>Lighting, boundaries &amp; street furniture</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What matters</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Built around your<br>building.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Built around trading</span></h4><ul><li>Phased around live trading &amp; service</li><li>Rooms &amp; areas out of service minimised</li><li>Out-of-hours &amp; overnight working</li><li>Brand &amp; guest-experience standards held throughout</li><li>Fast turnarounds between bookings &amp; seasons</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Compliance, handled</span></h4><ul><li>CDM 2015 throughout</li><li>Building Regs Part B (fire) &amp; Part E (acoustics)</li><li>Kitchen extract to DW/172</li><li>Water hygiene to HSG274</li><li>BS 7671 electrical certification</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you work around live trading and guests?</summary><p>Yes — most hospitality projects are phased around a venue that's still open. We plan out-of-hours and overnight works, temporary services and area-by-area handover so trading carries on and guests barely notice we're there.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you deliver to brand and operator standards?</summary><p>Yes. We build to the operator's brand book and fit-out guide — finishes, joinery, lighting and FF&amp;E held to spec — so the venue hands over on standard and on brand.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover commercial kitchen extract and ventilation?</summary><p>Yes. Kitchen extract, make-up air and ventilation are core MEPH for us, designed and installed to DW/172 so the kitchen passes inspection and runs comfortably under service.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>How fast can you turn around a refurbishment?</summary><p>Fast — we pin long-lead items at design stage and run a buildable programme around your trading and seasonal windows, with one project manager accountable for the reopening date.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Our service lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span class="ol-nm">MEPH</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial Fit-out</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Landscaping</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Talk to us about MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Scope, programme,<br>stage — send it over.</h2><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-top: 16px;">A named contact, not a sales team, comes back within 24 hours. Include the package, programme and stage if you can.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Enquire about MEPH →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/compliance/">Compliance &amp; BSA</a></div></div></div></section></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{@site.url}}/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Sectors", "item": "{{@site.url}}/sectors/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Hospitality & Leisure", "item": "